com.newrelic.pagerduty
Class Incident

java.lang.Object
  com.newrelic.pagerduty.Incident

public class Incident
extends Object

Represents a PageDuty incident. Create an instance and use it in in the trigger as well as acknowledge and resolve messages. The incident takes details but as near as I can tell this information isn't recorded by PagerDuty right now.
